        <abstract> 
<p>CD, commenting on a case of peloric flowering in <hi rend="italic">Auricula</hi>, urges readers to send in their observations on whether flowers nearest the axis tend to differ from others on the plant. Such a law of variation would be worth discovering.</p> 
        </abstract>
